
*** DRAFT ***

Building and Installing Oil
===========================

(This file is packaged with the Oil source release, oil.tar.)


System Requirements
-------------------

- C compiler (C89 ?)
- Bourne shell (POSIX)
- GNU Make (for now)

Optional:

- GNU readline library   OR
- libedit?  (NOTE: dash supports it.)

Instructions
------------

    ./configure [--prefix=PREFIX] [--without-readline]
      --lto
      --pgo
    make
    sudo make install

